"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/60/37834?source=related_link\">",
"      Pharmacotherapy of allergic rhinitis",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
